data.description: SUPER NICE LOCATION!! This Beautiful Brick Home features a Large Master bedroom, 2.5 baths and a huge bonus room over the garage that could be used as a bedroom, Stainless Steel appliances, open concept, Oversized living room w/gas Fireplace, A formal dining room, New Hardwood flooring, Recently Painted, New HVAC Unit, New deck, New Roof replaced this year. All New light Fixtures, Large bedrooms with walk in closets, A beautiful Huge Back Yard w/ Mature trees and Privacy Fence, convenient to HWY-24, Shopping, and minutes away from Ft. Campbell. Home is located in a cul-de-sac! P.S. Early Occupancy possible ! Seller will pay $12,000 Towards Buyers CLOSING COST!!!
